{"tid":1267150,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[請巴絲推] 有關新會員問題","createTime":"2019-06-29T17:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T02:02:59.000Z","uid":251086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8748f485c85c7033bc15055392807c5ea69d87","tid":1267150,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"大家好多時都話好多新會員開post帶風向，但個個就去回膠post，罵戰，變相係咁推post，上晒熱門真係多得大家唔少<br />\n<br />\n其實，大家可以在回覆前起佢底，睇下係咪假膠，之後可以覆<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">請善用起底功能，假膠，勿推</span></span>，等其他人知，唔好再push。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起碼各巴絲一齊努力，減少假膠同放負既post上黎，讓佢沉，等d有用既戰略post上熱門<br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2ccbea625702d833d79c6927d0bfe785df3b37","tid":1267150,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:56:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fe3606228a9b167de67adfab8d1ea856e481f0","tid":1267150,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:57:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85db2836d3636f094b030dfc98b3d744394c8a03","tid":1267150,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6ogywo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6ogywo.png&h=a84d61c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec7eee3032c19e020fff2e8397651ce175450d97","tid":1267150,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85db2836d3636f094b030dfc98b3d744394c8a03",